"Accepts any date in any <a "
"href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/tar/manual/html_chapter/tar_7.html#Date-input-formats\">GNU "
"Date Input Format</a>. Strings such as today, +2 months, and Dec 9 "
"2004 are all valid."
msgstr ""
"Accepte n'importe quelle date dans n'importe quel <a "
"href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/tar/manual/html_chapter/tar_7.html#Date-input-formats\">format "
"d'entrée de la date GNU</a>. Des chaînes telles que today, +2 "
"months, et Dec 9 2004 sont toutes valides."

