"Time format is only applicable for browsers that do not have support "
"for the HTML5 time element. Browsers that support the HTML5 time "
"element will display the time using the user's preferred format."
msgstr ""
"Le format de l'heure ne s'applique qu'aux navigateurs qui ne prennent "
"pas en charge l'élément temporel HTML5. Les navigateurs qui prennent "
"en charge l'élément HTML5 time afficheront l'heure en utilisant le "
