"Rating plugin for jQuery. Fast, progressive enhancement, touch "
"support, customizable (just swap out the images, or change some CSS), "
"unobtrusive JavaScript (using HTML5 data-* attributes), RTL support. "
"The Rating plugin supports as many stars as you'd like, and also any "
"step size."
msgstr ""
"Plugin de notation pour jQuery. Rapide, amélioration progressive, "
"support tactile, personnalisable (il suffit de changer les images ou "
"de modifier quelques CSS), JavaScript discret (utilisant les attributs "
"HTML5 data-*), support RTL. Le plugin Rating supporte autant "
"d'étoiles que vous le souhaitez, ainsi que n'importe quelle taille de "
"pas."

msgid ""
"Select2 gives you a customizable select box with support for searching "
"and tagging."
msgstr ""
"Select2 vous offre une boîte de sélection personnalisable avec prise "
"en charge de la recherche et du marquage."

